{"about_the_game":"<strong> &quot;Armor of Doom&quot; is a fascinating TPS game with &quot;tank vehicle&quot; + &quot;MOBA&quot; gameplay. </strong><br><strong> A variety of tank types are available for players to choose from, including light tanks, medium tanks, heavy tanks, anti-tanks, etc. </strong><br><strong> The game takes diversified strategy combinations and teamwork as its core, providing players with a real and brutal battlefield fighting experience. </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various tank types</h2>Players can choose from multiple different tank types, including light tanks, medium tanks, heavy tanks, anti-tanks, etc. Each tank has its own unique characteristics and positioning. Players can choose the right tank according to their personal style and tactical needs, and build a strong team with their teammates.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/extras/tank01.gif?t=1728996523\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Techniques and tactics</h2>The game emphasizes personal skill and tactical resourcefulness. Players need to learn to target the enemy's weaknesses and use skills and buffs appropriately to cause maximum damage. At the same time, players need to master hiding skills and formulate response strategies by analyzing the opponent's tank type and tactical intentions.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/extras/tank04.gif?t=1728996523\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse game modes:</h2>Provides multiple game modes such as single player matching and team matching battles. Whether playing alone or in a team, players can enjoy a challenging and exciting gaming experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/extras/tank05.gif?t=1728996523\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Personalized development system:</h2>In-game development: Players can obtain resources during battles and use them to upgrade different attributes of tanks to adapt to the changing battlefield environment.<br>Outside development: Unlock new accessories, choose crew members, and customize tank capabilities according to your personal style to enhance combat effectiveness.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/extras/tank02.gif?t=1728996523\" /><br><br>These features together constitute the unique gaming experience of &quot;Armor of Doom&quot;, aiming to provide players with a rich gaming battlefield full of strategy and skills.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728996523","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/page.bg.jpg?t=1728996523","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728996523","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902000/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728996523","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong> &quot;Armor of Doom&quot; is a fascinating TPS game with &quot;tank vehicle&quot; + &quot;MOBA&quot; gameplay. </strong><br><strong> A variety of tank types are available for players to choose from, including light tanks, medium tanks, heavy tanks, anti-tanks, etc. </strong><br><strong> The game takes diversified strategy combinations and teamwork as its core, providing players with a real and brutal battlefield fighting experience. </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various tank types</h2>Players can choose from multiple different tank types, including light tanks, medium tanks, heavy tanks